headline: Banking on Yield? Here’s How We Scored Dime Community Bancshares (DCOM) Dividend
summary: Regional banks continued their steady dividend payouts this week, with Dime Community Bancshares (NASDAQ: DCOM) paying 25 cents per share on Jan. 23, maintaining the quarterly rate it’s held since early 2023.
